# ============================================================
# TREISHVAAM FINANCE FRONTEND — .gitignore
# ============================================================
# AI-CONTEXT:
# Purpose: Prevent sensitive, generated, and AI session files from entering git.
# Security: .env variants, AI instruction folders, and stray documents
#           must NEVER be committed.
#
# IMMUTABLE CHANGE HISTORY (DO NOT DELETE):
# - ADDED: Initial .gitignore for CRA.
# - EDITED: Added AI instruction folders and RULES OF ENGAGEMENT.
# - EDITED: Added HANDOVER_DOCUMENT.md and FINANCE_BUG_ANALYSIS.md.
# - EDITED (2026-05-25 / Docs Restructure Phase):
#   • Consolidated .gitignore-additions.md content into this file.
#   • Deleted .gitignore-additions.md (content absorbed, file no longer needed).
#   • Added: docs_file_list.json (Windows PS artifact — exposes local paths, security risk).
#   • Added: "New Text Document.txt" and *.txt catch-all for stray text files.
#   • Added: .roo/state/ (Roo Code session state — not for git).
#   • Added: build/ (CRA legacy build artifact — must not be in git).
#   • Added: fix-encoding.js (one-time encoding fix script — target file exists, script obsolete).
#   • Added: postcss.config.js (legacy CRA duplicate of postcss.config.mjs — deleted).
#   • Added: !.env.example exception to keep the safe template.

# ============================================================
# DEPENDENCIES
# ============================================================
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.js

# ============================================================
# TESTING
# ============================================================
/coverage

# ============================================================
# BUILD ARTIFACTS — NEVER COMMIT THESE
# ============================================================
/build
/out
.next/
.vercel/

# ============================================================
# ENVIRONMENT & SECRETS — NEVER COMMIT THESE
# ============================================================
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.development.local
.env.production
.env.production.local
.env.test.local
# Keep the example template (contains no real values)
!.env.example

# ============================================================
# LOGS
# ============================================================
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ============================================================
# OS FILES
# ============================================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ============================================================
# IDE
# ============================================================
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/
*.iml

# ============================================================
# AI SESSION & INSTRUCTION FOLDERS — NEVER COMMIT THESE
# These folders hold session-level AI context and architecture secrets.
# ============================================================
RULES OF ENGAGEMENT & AI INSTRUCTIONS & EDITS/
BACKEND_CODE_FILES/
BACKEND CODE FILES/

# ============================================================
# STRAY / ONE-TIME / TEMPORARY FILES — NEVER COMMIT THESE
# ============================================================
HANDOVER_DOCUMENT.md
HANDOVER_DOCUMENT_TEMPLATE.md
FINANCE_BUG_ANALYSIS.md
ARCHITECTURE_QUICKREF.md
TODO.md
docs_file_list.json
New Text Document.txt
fix-encoding.js
*.txt

# ============================================================
# LEGACY CRA ARTIFACTS (superseded by Next.js equivalents)
# ============================================================
# postcss.config.mjs is the correct ESM version — .js is CRA legacy duplicate
postcss.config.js

# ============================================================
# AI TOOL STATE
# ============================================================
# Roo Code session state (AI rules are kept, session state is local-only)
.roo/state/
